headline: Electro Switch Appoints Shawn Smith as Chief Executive Officer and Matt Yopchick as Chief Financial Officer
summary: WEYMOUTH, Mass., December 11, 2025--At Electro Switch, Shawn Smith is the new CEO and Matt Yopchick is the new CFO.
